{{Function |origin = GECK1 |summary = Returns 1 if the [[actor]] is currently running the specified [[package]], 0 otherwise. |name = GetIsCurrentPackage |returnType = boolean |referenceType = actorRef |arguments = {{FunctionArgument |Name = AIPackage |Type = form }} |example = ActorRef.GetIsCurrentPackage AnvilGuardPatrolDay8x7 }}
==See Also== *[[GetBasePackages]] *[[GetCurrentAIPackage]] *[[GetCurrentPackage]] *[[GetPackageCount]]
