{{Function |CSWikiPage = GetIsCurrentWeather |origin = GECK1 |summary = Returns 1 if the current weather is active |name = GetIsCurrentWeather |returnType = bool |arguments = {{FunctionArgument |Name = weather |Type = ref }} |example = GetIsCurrentWeather WastelandClear Checks if the active weather is WastelandClear and returns 1 if true.
}}
==See Also== *[[GetCurrentWeather]] Doesn't require checking explicit weather REF IDS and instead returns the current weather, making it much more versatile
[[Category:Functions (GECK)]] [[Category:Functions]] [[Category:Weather Functions]] [[Category:Functions (FO3)]] [[Category:Condition Functions]]

{{Function |origin = GECK1 |summary = Returns a number indicating the last limb that was hit (dismembered, exploded, or intact) when the referenced actor was killed. |name = GetKillingBlowLimb |returnType = limb:int |referenceType = [actor:reference] |example = if BuddyRef.GetKillingBlowLimb == 0 This would determine if Buddy was killed by a hit to the torso. }} ==Notes== {| {{Wikitable}} ! Body Part !! Return Value |- | None | -1 |- | Torso | 0 |- | Head 1 | 1 |- | Head 2 | 2 |- | Left Arm 1 | 3 |- | Left Arm 2 | 4 |- | Right Arm 1 | 5 |- | Right Arm 2 | 6 |- | Left Leg 1 | 7 |- | Left Leg 2 | 8 |- | Left Leg 3 | 9 |- | Right Leg 1 | 10 |- | Right Leg 2 | 11 |- | Right Leg 3 | 12 |- | Brain | 13 |- | Hand or Weapon | 14 |}
==See Also== *[[GetCauseofDeath]] *[[GetHitLocation]] *[[IsLimbGone]]
[[Category:Functions (GECK)]] [[Category:Functions]] [[Category:Condition Functions]] [[Category:Functions (FO3)]]

{{Function |origin = GECK1 |summary = Returns the index of the last action performed by the player. |returnType = int |example = GetLastPlayerAction Returns the index of the last action performed by the player }} {{:ActionIndex}}
